stateDiagram-v2
    %% REQ-1: FAIL_OPEN除去 - Hook Error Handling States
    [*] --> HookExecution

    HookExecution --> ErrorOccurred: Exception raised
    HookExecution --> NoError: All checks pass

    ErrorOccurred --> CheckFailOpen: Check FAIL_OPEN flag
    CheckFailOpen --> FailOpenEnabled: FAIL_OPEN=true
    CheckFailOpen --> FailOpenDisabled: FAIL_OPEN not set/false

    FailOpenEnabled --> PassThrough: (OLD: Exit 0)
    PassThrough --> PermitOperation: DEPRECATED (REQ-1)

    FailOpenDisabled --> Exit2: Exit with code 2
    Exit2 --> BlockOperation: REJECT (secure)

    %% REQ-1 enforced state
    ErrorOccurred_REQ1 --> AlwaysExit2: Always exit(2)
    AlwaysExit2 --> BlockOperation

    NoError --> PermitOperation: (REQ-1: normal flow)
    BlockOperation --> [*]
    PermitOperation --> [*]

    %% REQ-2: HMAC State File Integrity States
    [*] --> WorkflowStateAccess

    WorkflowStateAccess --> ReadStateFile: Load workflow-state.json

    ReadStateFile --> StateFileFound: File exists
    ReadStateFile --> StateFileNotFound: File not found

    StateFileNotFound --> CreateNewState: Initialize new state
    CreateNewState --> StateUnsigned: No signature (initial)

    StateFileFound --> ParseJSON: Parse JSON content
    ParseJSON --> JSONValid: Valid JSON
    ParseJSON --> JSONInvalid: JSON parse error

    JSONInvalid --> SignatureVerificationFailed: Corrupted file
    SignatureVerificationFailed --> ReturnNull: Return null

    JSONValid --> CheckSignatureField: Check stateIntegrity field

    CheckSignatureField --> SignaturePresent: stateIntegrity exists
    CheckSignatureField --> SignatureAbsent: No signature field

    SignatureAbsent --> StateUnsigned: Legacy format (backward compat)
    StateUnsigned --> AutoAddSignature: Add signature on first access
    AutoAddSignature --> SignatureGenerated: HMAC-SHA256 computed

    SignaturePresent --> VerifyHMAC: Validate signature
    VerifyHMAC --> SignatureValid: HMAC matches
    VerifyHMAC --> SignatureTampered: HMAC mismatch

    SignatureTampered --> ReturnNull: Reject: file modified
    SignatureValid --> StateIntact: State is trusted
    SignatureGenerated --> StateIntact: State is trusted

    StateIntact --> UpdateOperation: Can proceed
    UpdateOperation --> WriteTaskState: Save updated state
    WriteTaskState --> GenerateNewSignature: Compute HMAC
    GenerateNewSignature --> StoreWithSignature: Save with signature
    StoreWithSignature --> [*]

    ReturnNull --> [*]

    %% REQ-3: Scope Validation States
    [*] --> ScopeDefinition

    ScopeDefinition --> SetScopeOperation: workflowSetScope() called
    SetScopeOperation --> ValidatePhase: Check current phase

    ValidatePhase --> PhaseAllowed: research/requirements/planning
    ValidatePhase --> PhaseNotAllowed: Other phase

    PhaseNotAllowed --> RejectScope: Error: wrong phase
    RejectScope --> [*]

    PhaseAllowed --> CalculateScopeSize: Count files and dirs
    CalculateScopeSize --> FileCountCheck: Compare file count

    FileCountCheck --> FilesWithinLimit: files ≤ 200
    FileCountCheck --> FileCountExceeded: files > 200

    FileCountExceeded --> SuggestSplit: Recommend task split
    SuggestSplit --> RejectScope

    FilesWithinLimit --> DirectoryCountCheck: Compare dir count
    DirectoryCountCheck --> DirsWithinLimit: dirs ≤ 20
    DirectoryCountCheck --> DirCountExceeded: dirs > 20

    DirCountExceeded --> SuggestSplit

    DirsWithinLimit --> ScopeAccepted: Size within limits
    ScopeAccepted --> SaveToTaskState: Store scope
    SaveToTaskState --> [*]

    %% Scope Validation on Phase Transition (parallel_analysis → parallel_design)
    [*] --> NextPhaseExecution
    NextPhaseExecution --> CheckCurrentPhase_Scope: Is parallel_analysis?

    CheckCurrentPhase_Scope --> NotParallelAnalysis: Other phase
    NotParallelAnalysis --> ContinueTransition: Proceed normally

    CheckCurrentPhase_Scope --> IsParallelAnalysis: parallel_analysis phase
    IsParallelAnalysis --> ValidateScopeOnTransition: Check scope size
    ValidateScopeOnTransition --> ScopeValidOnTransition: Size OK
    ValidateScopeOnTransition --> ScopeInvalidOnTransition: Size exceeded

    ScopeInvalidOnTransition --> BlockTransition: Error: reconfigure scope
    BlockTransition --> [*]

    ScopeValidOnTransition --> ContinueTransition
    ContinueTransition --> [*]

    %% REQ-4: Bash Command Analysis States
    [*] --> BashExecution

    BashExecution --> AnalyzeBashCommand: analyzeBashCommand(cmd)
    AnalyzeBashCommand --> SplitCommand: splitCompoundCommand()

    SplitCommand --> CheckOperators: Find &&, ||, ;, |
    CheckOperators --> NoCompoundOperators: Simple command
    CheckOperators --> HasCompoundOperators: Multi-part command

    NoCompoundOperators --> SinglePartArray: ['cmd']
    SinglePartArray --> ProcessParts: Validate each part

    HasCompoundOperators --> SplitMultipart: ['cmd1', 'cmd2', ...]
    SplitMultipart --> ProcessParts

    ProcessParts --> CheckPart1: Validate part 1
    CheckPart1 --> Part1ReadOnly: Is read-only command
    CheckPart1 --> Part1NotReadOnly: Not in whitelist

    Part1ReadOnly --> AllowPart1: Continue to next part
    AllowPart1 --> CheckPart2: Validate part 2

    Part1NotReadOnly --> CheckFileModifying1: Check file modify patterns
    CheckFileModifying1 --> Part1ModifiesFiles: Matches rm, sed, awk>, etc.
    CheckFileModifying1 --> Part1NoModify: No file operations

    Part1ModifiesFiles --> BlockCommand: Blocked: file modification
    BlockCommand --> [*]

    Part1NoModify --> AllowPart1

    CheckPart2 --> Part2ReadOnly: Is read-only
    CheckPart2 --> Part2NotReadOnly: Not in whitelist

    Part2ReadOnly --> AllowPart2: Continue to part 3
    AllowPart2 --> CheckPart3: Validate part 3

    Part2NotReadOnly --> CheckFileModifying2: Check file modify patterns
    CheckFileModifying2 --> Part2ModifiesFiles: Matches patterns
    CheckFileModifying2 --> Part2NoModify: No file operations

    Part2ModifiesFiles --> BlockCommand
    Part2NoModify --> AllowPart2

    CheckPart3 --> AllPartsProcessed: All parts validated
    AllPartsProcessed --> AllPartsReadOnlyOrWhitelisted: All OK
    AllPartsReadOnlyOrWhitelisted --> AllowExecution: Permit command
    AllowExecution --> [*]

    %% REQ-5: Artifact Validation States
    [*] --> ArtifactCheck

    ArtifactCheck --> GetPhaseArtifacts: Get required files for phase
    GetPhaseArtifacts --> CheckFileExistence: Verify file exists

    CheckFileExistence --> FileMissing: File not found
    CheckFileExistence --> FileExists: File present

    FileMissing --> AddToMissingList: Record missing file
    AddToMissingList --> [*]

    FileExists --> ReadFileContent: Load file content
    ReadFileContent --> ContentReadSuccess: File readable
    ReadFileContent --> ContentReadFailure: Read error

    ContentReadFailure --> AddToInvalidList: Record read error
    AddToInvalidList --> [*]

    ContentReadSuccess --> ValidateSize: Check file size ≥ 200 bytes
    ValidateSize --> SizeOK: Size sufficient
    ValidateSize --> SizeTooSmall: Size < 200 bytes

    SizeTooSmall --> AddSizeError: Record size error
    AddSizeError --> [*]

    SizeOK --> CheckRequiredSections: Look for mandatory sections
    CheckRequiredSections --> SectionFound: Has required section
    CheckRequiredSections --> SectionNotFound: Missing required section

    SectionNotFound --> AddSectionError: Record section error
    AddSectionError --> [*]

    SectionFound --> CheckForbiddenPatterns: Detect stubs
    CheckForbiddenPatterns --> ForbiddenFound: "TODO", "WIP", etc.
    CheckForbiddenPatterns --> NoForbidden: No stubs detected

    ForbiddenFound --> AddStubError: Record stub detection
    AddStubError --> [*]

    NoForbidden --> CheckHeaderOnly: Verify not headers-only
    CheckHeaderOnly --> HasContent: Has actual content
    CheckHeaderOnly --> OnlyHeaders: Only header lines

    OnlyHeaders --> AddHeaderError: Record header-only error
    AddHeaderError --> [*]

    HasContent --> ArtifactValid: All validations pass
    ArtifactValid --> AllArtifactsValid: Check all required files

    AllArtifactsValid --> MissingOrInvalid: Have errors?
    MissingOrInvalid --> YesErrors: missing.length > 0 OR invalid.length > 0
    MissingOrInvalid --> NoErrors: All files valid

    YesErrors --> BlockCommit: Block pre-commit hook
    BlockCommit --> [*]

    NoErrors --> AllowCommit: Permit operation
    AllowCommit --> [*]

    %% REQ-6: Design Validation States
    [*] --> DesignValidation

    DesignValidation --> CheckCurrentPhase_Design: Is parallel_design phase?
    CheckCurrentPhase_Design --> NotDesignPhase: Other phase
    NotDesignPhase --> SkipDesignValidation: Continue

    CheckCurrentPhase_Design --> IsDesignPhase: parallel_design
    IsDesignPhase --> TransitionTarget: Next phase is test_design?

    TransitionTarget --> NotToTestDesign: No
    NotToTestDesign --> SkipDesignValidation

    TransitionTarget --> ToTestDesign: Yes, parallel_design → test_design
    ToTestDesign --> EnforceValidation: REQ-6: Always validate

    EnforceValidation --> CheckSkipEnvVar: Check SKIP_DESIGN_VALIDATION
    CheckSkipEnvVar --> SkipEnvVarSet: Env var = 'true'
    CheckSkipEnvVar --> SkipEnvVarNotSet: Env var not set

    SkipEnvVarSet --> ValidateAnyway: REQ-6: Ignore env var
    SkipEnvVarNotSet --> RunValidator: Execute validation
    ValidateAnyway --> RunValidator

    RunValidator --> GetScopeFiles: Get files in scope
    GetScopeFiles --> IterateSourceFiles: Process each file

    IterateSourceFiles --> CheckEmptyMethods: Pattern 1: method() {}
    CheckEmptyMethods --> EmptyMethodFound: Found empty method
    CheckEmptyMethods --> NoEmptyMethod: No empty methods

    EmptyMethodFound --> RecordStub1: Add to stub list
    RecordStub1 --> [*]

    NoEmptyMethod --> CheckTODOComments: Pattern 2: TODO/FIXME/NotImplemented
    CheckTODOComments --> TodoFound: Found TODO/FIXME
    CheckTODOComments --> NoTodo: No stub comments

    TodoFound --> RecordStub2: Add to stub list
    RecordStub2 --> [*]

    NoTodo --> CheckEmptyClasses: Pattern 3: class Foo {}
    CheckEmptyClasses --> EmptyClassFound: Found empty class
    CheckEmptyClasses --> NoEmptyClass: No empty classes

    EmptyClassFound --> RecordStub3: Add to stub list
    RecordStub3 --> [*]

    NoEmptyClass --> CheckNotImplemented: Pattern 4: throw NotImplementedError
    CheckNotImplemented --> NotImplFound: Found NotImplementedError
    CheckNotImplemented --> NoNotImpl: No NotImplementedError

    NotImplFound --> RecordStub4: Add to stub list
    RecordStub4 --> [*]

    NoNotImpl --> ProcessNextFile: Move to next source file
    ProcessNextFile --> AllFilesProcessed: All files checked

    AllFilesProcessed --> EvaluateResults: Assess stub findings
    EvaluateResults --> StubsDetected: missingItems.length > 0
    EvaluateResults --> NoStubsDetected: No stubs found

    StubsDetected --> SetValidationFailed: passed = false
    SetValidationFailed --> ReportStubs: Show detailed errors
    ReportStubs --> BlockPhaseTransition: Cannot enter test_design
    BlockPhaseTransition --> [*]

    NoStubsDetected --> CheckExistingDesignDocs: Verify spec/diagrams
    CheckExistingDesignDocs --> DesignDocsValid: All documents OK
    CheckExistingDesignDocs --> DesignDocsMissing: Missing documents

    DesignDocsMissing --> ReportMissing: Show missing docs
    ReportMissing --> BlockPhaseTransition

    DesignDocsValid --> SetValidationPassed: passed = true
    SetValidationPassed --> AllowTransition: Permit test_design entry
    AllowTransition --> SkipDesignValidation

    SkipDesignValidation --> [*]

    %% Notes and explanations
    note right of ErrorOccurred
        REQ-1: Hook error handling
        All errors must exit(2)
        FAIL_OPEN removed
    end note

    note right of SignatureTampered
        REQ-2: HMAC verification failed
        Indicates manual file edit
        Reject state access
    end note

    note right of FileCountExceeded
        REQ-3: Scope size exceeded
        Max 200 files, 20 dirs
        Recommend task split
    end note

    note right of Part1ModifiesFiles
        REQ-4: Bash command analysis
        Detect file modifications
        in compound commands
    end note

    note right of SizeTooSmall
        REQ-5: Artifact validation
        Minimum 200 bytes
        Must have required sections
    end note

    note right of StubsDetected
        REQ-6: Design validation
        Detect empty implementations
        Block phase transition
    end note
